Package: NatureDataCubeR
Type: Package
Title: Programmatic and graphical interfaces to LTER-LIFE's NatureDataCube
Version: 0.3
Date: 2026-06-12
Author: Bruno Marcos, Daan Lichtenberg, Minke Mulder
Maintainer: Bruno Marcos <brunoasmarcos@gmail.com>, Daan Lichtenberg <D.Lichtenberg@nioo.knaw.nl>
Description: A set of functions, wrappers, and a Shiny app GUI to facilitate finding and getting data from LTER-LIFE's NatureDataCube.
